@ks: I just followed the instructions on the wiki, I left everything stock basically:

https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Infinality

There's an important part in the wiki that probably isn't as clear as it should be - the metapackages for fonts are not supposed to be installed - they have conflicting packages inside them and are more to be grouped together so you can see what's available. I just installed `ibfonts-meta-extended`.
